{
  "id": "adv_group_liz_03_05",
  "title": "LizNoir 03 05",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cafe-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ莉央、こんな所でのんびりしてていいの？\n僕達もっと練習した方がいいんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey Rio‚ are you sure it's okay for us to be relaxing here?\nShouldn't we be practicing more?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 7.6634012222290036,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "たまには息抜きも必要なの。最近、葵は根を詰め過ぎよ\n明らかにオーバーワークだし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You need to take breaks sometimes. You've been pushing yourself too hard lately‚ Aoi.\nYou're clearly overworking yourself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.866666666666666,
      "endTime": 15.524172465006512,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.86666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.800000150998398
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……こんな女の子達が来る店\n僕には似合わないと思うんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa… I don't think this kind of girly cafe\nsuits me at all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.800000150998398,
      "endTime": 22.650000341733264,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "何言ってるのよ\n貴方、女の子でしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you talking about?\nYou’re a girl.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.833333484331742,
      "endTime": 26.033333579699175,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.23333348433174
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、そっか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ right.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.23333348433174,
      "endTime": 27.73333348433174,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.933333484331737
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "……一応聞くけど\nそのリアクションは冗談よね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……I'll ask just in case‚\nbut that reaction was a joke‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.933333484331737,
      "endTime": 31.655941144625316,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.83333348433174,
      "endTime": 33.36666681766507,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.73333348433173
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "はあ、全く……\n慣れていく自分が嫌だわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa‚ seriously……\nI hate that I’m getting used to this……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.73333348433173,
      "endTime": 39.333333484331725,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "葵、メニューよ\n私が奢るからなんでも好きなものを頼みなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi‚ here’s the menu.\nI’m treating you‚ so order whatever you like.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.53333333333333,
      "endTime": 44.54616784254706,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.53333348433173
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.733333484331745
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "お冷やかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Water‚ please.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.733333484331745,
      "endTime": 46.333333484331746,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.56666681766509
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "……あのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……Um‚ listen.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.56666681766509,
      "endTime": 47.76666679382323,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "これも冗談だよ\n莉央と同じでいい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m just kidding.\nI’ll have the same as you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.96666679382323,
      "endTime": 50.697188282012924,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "分かったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.89627825419105,
      "endTime": 52.79627825419105,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.02961158752439
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "……ふう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……Huu.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.02961158752439,
      "endTime": 54.59627825419106,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.6296115875244
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.6296115875244
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "krk",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kiriko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05-krk001.m4a",
      "text": "もし優勝出来なかったら\nLizNoirは解散よ――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you don’t win‚\nLizNoir will disband――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.69627825419105,
      "endTime": 61.96294492085773,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.1629449208577
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.7296115875244
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "……霧子\nそれ本当に社長が言ったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……Himeno-san.\nDid the president really say that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.7296115875244,
      "endTime": 67.19983816146849,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.39627825419106
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "krk",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kiriko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05-krk002.m4a",
      "text": "そうよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.39627825419106,
      "endTime": 68.3296115875244,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "僕達は十分、バンプロに貢献してると思うけど\nそれでも？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think we’ve contributed enough to Vanpro‚\nbut even then?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.59627825419105,
      "endTime": 73.69627825419104,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.06294492085772
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "krk",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kiriko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05-krk003.m4a",
      "text": "社長はナンバーワンにしか興味はないのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The president is only interested in number one.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.06294492085772,
      "endTime": 77.02961158752439,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "……そう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……I see.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.29627825419104,
      "endTime": 78.52961158752437,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.86294492085773
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "krk",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kiriko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05-krk004.m4a",
      "text": "もう貴方達の退路は断たれたわ\n何がなんでも優勝しなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You have no way out now.\nYou have to win no matter what.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.86294492085773,
      "endTime": 83.4763237317403,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.69627825419103
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "分かったよ\n霧子、一つだけお願いがある",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand.\nHimeno-san‚ I have one request.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.69627825419103,
      "endTime": 87.52961158752434,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.72961158752436
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_05-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "解散のことは、莉央には話さないで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please don't tell Rio about the disbandment.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.72961158752436,
      "endTime": 90.54255938529963,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.92961158752435
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "krk",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kiriko.png",
